title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show APR-21-2014 MON
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show APR-21-2014 MON...PODCAST


The Glenn Beck Program



 The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program 4/21/14Monday, April 21, 2014 


Glenn wishes everyone a Happy Tax Freedom Day,

 warns Americans about the direction food prices are in (hint: it isn't down!)

     and covers a Utah state representative's plan to get federal lands
          back into the hands of the states. 

Also, Pastor Todd Burpo joins the program to discuss "Heaven Is For Real"

    and Bryan Smith joins Glenn to discuss his run for US Congress.

         That and more on The Glenn Beck Program!
